<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="wish-v">wish <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /wɪʃ/    美 /wɪʃ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>[后接表示虚拟语气的从句]要是...就好了：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I wish I were taller. 
我要是个子高一些就好了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I wish I didn’t have to work today. 
要是今天我不用工作就好了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I wish I had taken your advice. 
我当初要是采纳了你的建议就好了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I wish I could speak French. 
我要是能讲法语就好了。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>想；希望：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You may leave now, <strong>if you wish</strong>. 
如果你想走，现在就可以走了。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>wish to do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Anyone wishing to try race walking should first consult a coach.
任何想要尝试竞走的人应该首先咨询教练。</p><footer>2020全国改</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>wish sb to do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Why don’t you wish your son to accept this post? 
你为什么不希望儿子接受这个职位呢?</p></div>

<ul>
<li>wish sth done:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I wish the problem settled. 
我希望这个问题已经得到解决。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>祝愿：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Finally, I rose to leave, <strong>wished</strong> him <strong>well</strong>, and headed for the exit. 
最后，我站起身来，说了一些祝福他的话，然后向出口走去。</p><footer>2010 重庆</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I wish you every success. 
祝你万事如意。</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>盼望；想要：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It's no use <strong>wishing for</strong> the impossible.
企求不可能的事情是无用的。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Ellen is a fantastic dancer. I wish I <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (dance) as well as her.  （2015 陕西改）  </li>
<li>I wish I <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (be) at my sister’s wedding last Tuesday, but I was on a business trip in New York then.  （2015 天津改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. danced  2. had been  </p></div>